---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Celigo Integration" description="Official Celigo partner with deep Acumatica expertise. Enterprise iPaaS integrations built right.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-teal font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-4">Official Celigo Partner</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">
          Celigo + Acumatica.<br />
          <span class="text-teal">Done by someone who knows both.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Most Celigo partners know iPaaS. Most Acumatica consultants know ERP.
          We're one of the few who know both deeply — so your integrations
          actually work the way your business does.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What is Celigo -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-4">Why Celigo?</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Celigo is an enterprise integration platform (iPaaS) that connects
            Acumatica to hundreds of apps — CRM, ecommerce, shipping, payroll,
            and more — without fragile custom code.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            It's built for business users to monitor and manage, but it takes
            an expert to set up correctly. A bad integration is worse than no
            integration — it creates data you can't trust.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-warm">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Pre-built connectors</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Hundreds of pre-built integrations for popular platforms, customized to your specific workflow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-warm">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Error handling built in</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Automatic retries, error dashboards, and alerting so issues get caught before they cause damage.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-warm">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Scalable and maintainable</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Unlike custom scripts, Celigo flows can be monitored, modified, and maintained by your team long-term.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Common Integrations -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-gray-warm">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <p class="text-teal font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-3">Common Integrations</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy">
          Connect Acumatica to the tools you already use.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">CRM Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Salesforce, HubSpot, and other CRM platforms synced bidirectionally with Acumatica.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Ecommerce</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Shopify, BigCommerce, WooCommerce — orders, inventory, and customers in sync.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Shipping & Logistics</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">ShipStation, FedEx, UPS — automated label generation and tracking updates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Payroll & HR</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">ADP, Paychex, and other payroll systems integrated for seamless financial data flow.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Warehouse Management</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">WMS platforms connected for real-time inventory accuracy and order fulfillment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Custom & Legacy</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">REST APIs, flat files, FTP — if it has data, we can connect it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-navy">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">
        Need to connect Acumatica to something?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Let's talk about what you're trying to connect and the simplest
        way to make it reliable.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold rounded-lg bg-teal text-white hover:bg-teal-dark transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
